OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA hot day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, staying a little cooler
OL,7,Falong the coast. The sunshine turning
OL,8,Fhazy at times. A gentle breeze
OL,9,Fstrengthens during the afternoon
OL,10,Fbefore easing by the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClouding over but remaining
OL,13,Fdry for most places, the odd spot of
OL,14,Frain possible across northern parts
OL,15,Flater in the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAny cloud and rain should
OL,18,Fclear during the morning to give a
OL,19,Fbright, sunny and hot day. Staying a
OL,20,Flittle cooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
